@startuml
skinparam componentStyle rectangle

|Query Analysis| as QA
|Candidate Retrieval| as CR
|Re-ranking| as RR
|Quality Assessment| as QA2
|Result Output| as RO

QA -> CR: User Intent
CR -> RR: Candidate Set
RR -> QA2: Ranked List
QA2 -> RO: Final Results

note left of CR
  Multi-channel recall:
  - Keyword recall
  - Vector recall
  - Graph recall
end note

note right of RR
  Cross-encoder reranking
  Learning to rank
end note

@enduml
